                <section>
                    <h2>DOOM FROM AN ALTERNATE UNIVERSE</h2>

                    <b>Nobody Told Me About id</b> is a love letter from DOOM
                    fans to the iconic trinity of Build Engine games; Duke Nukem
                    3D, Blood and Shadow Warrior. Whether it be ludicrous gibs
                    or explosions, NTMAi tries its best to faithfully replicate
                    all things Build on DOOM while also enhancing vanilla
                    gameplay. Your arsenal may be tough, but some enemies will
                    have a trick or two up their sleeves...<br /><br />
                    NTMAi originally started off as a small project during
                    summer 2019. It went on to
                    <a href="https://www.doomworld.com/cacowards/2020/gameplay/">win a Cacoward in 2020</a>
                    and eventually got rebooted to a much better state in early
                    2023.
                </section>

